        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "解：∵AB//CD $\\textcircled{1}P\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{A B}{C D}\\therefore A B=1,C D=2.A C=6$ ∴△AOB∽△COD $\\textcircled{1}P\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{A B}{C D}\\therefore A B=1,C D=2.A C=6$ \n$\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{1}{2}\\Rightarrow C O=2A O$ \n三$\\because\\frac{S_{\\Delta A O B}}{S_{\\Delta C O D}}=(\\frac{A B}{C D})^{2}=(\\frac{1}{2})^{2}=\\frac{1}{4}=\\frac{1}{S_{\\Delta C O D}}$ $S\\because A C=A O+C O=3A O\\Rightarrow3A O=6.A O=2$ $\\therefore S_{\\Delta C O D}=4$ S_BOc(不同底，同高)目底比为$O A:O C=1=2$ \n∴S△AOB $S_{\\Delta B O C}=1:2\\because S_{\\Delta A O B}=1$ $S_{\\Delta B O C}=2$ .同理：S△AOD与S△COD(不同底，同高\n且底之比为$O A:O C=1:2:S_{\\Delta A O D}:S_{\\Delta C O D}=1:2$ ",
          "block_bbox": [
            203,
