          "block_order": 3
        }
      ],
      "markdown": "## 54 \n\n/.如图，梯形ABCD中：AB∥∥CD.若AB=1.\n\nCD=2.AC=6.S△AOB=1.则AO=\n\nS梯形ABCD=\n\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_643_807_2187_1523.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"62%\" /></div>\n\n\n解：∵AB//CD $\\textcircled{1}P\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{A B}{C D}\\therefore A B=1,C D=2.A C=6$ ∴△AOB∽△COD $\\textcircled{1}P\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{A B}{C D}\\therefore A B=1,C D=2.A C=6$ \n\n$\\frac{A O}{C O}=\\frac{1}{2}\\Rightarrow C O=2A O$ \n\n三$\\because\\frac{S_{\\Delta A O B}}{S_{\\Delta C O D}}=(\\frac{A B}{C D})^{2}=(\\frac{1}{2})^{2}=\\frac{1}{4}=\\frac{1}{S_{\\Delta C O D}}$ $S\\because A C=A O+C O=3A O\\Rightarrow3A O=6.A O=2$ $\\therefore S_{\\Delta C O D}=4$ S_BOc(不同底，同高)目底比为$O A:O C=1=2$ \n\n∴S△AOB $S_{\\Delta B O C}=1:2\\because S_{\\Delta A O B}=1$ $S_{\\Delta B O C}=2$ .同理：S△AOD与S△COD(不同底，同高\n\n且底之比为$O A:O C=1:2:S_{\\Delta A O D}:S_{\\Delta C O D}=1:2$ ",
